        <mxCell id="FpkSZrteuwkwKbi4V13a-54" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=default;fillColor=default;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;strokeWidth=2;" value="&lt;p style=&quot;overflow-x: auto; box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 4px; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 8px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; style=&quot;background-color: light-dark(#ffffff, var(--ge-dark-color, #121212));&quot;&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;padding: 0px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;Network Architecture&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;font-size: 11px; padding: 0px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;font-size: 11px; padding: 0px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word;&quot;&gt;VLAN 10 (host server):    10.10.10.0/24&lt;br&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;font-size: 11px; padding: 0px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word;&quot;&gt;VLAN 20 (Admin):           10.20.20.0/24&lt;br&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;font-size: 11px; padding: 0px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word;&quot;&gt;VLAN 30 (Egress / WiFi):   192.168.1.0/24&lt;br&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;font-size: 11px; padding: 0px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word;&quot;&gt;WireGuard tunnel:          10.0.0.0/24&lt;br&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;font-size: 11px; padding: 0px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;padding: 0px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;Permitted Inter-VLAN Flows:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;font-size: 11px; padding: 0px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word;&quot;&gt;- VLAN 20 → VLAN 10:       SSH (22), Open WebUI (3000)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;font-size: 11px; padding: 0px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word;&quot;&gt;- VLAN 10/20 → Internet:   NAT via aegis eth0&lt;br&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;font-size: 11px; padding: 0px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word;&quot;&gt;- WireGuard → VLAN 10:     Open WebUI (3000)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;font-size: 11px; padding: 0px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word;&quot;&gt;- All VLANs → aegis:       DNS (53)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;font-size: 11px; padding: 0px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word;&quot;&gt;- VLAN 20 → aegis:         SSH (2222), Pi-hole admin (80)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;font-size: 11px; padding: 0px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word;&quot;&gt;- WireGuard → aegis:       SSH (2222), DNS (53)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;font-size: 11px; padding: 0px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;padding: 0px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;Blocked (default deny):&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;font-size: 11px; padding: 0px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word;&quot;&gt;- WiFi → VLAN 10/20 (no L3 route)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;font-size: 11px; padding: 0px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word;&quot;&gt;- VLAN 10 → VLAN 20 (no allow rule)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;font-size: 11px; padding: 0px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word;&quot;&gt;- Everything else not explicitly above&lt;br&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;font-size: 11px; padding: 0px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;font-size: 11px; padding: 0px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;R&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;padding: 0px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;emote Access Workflow:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;font-size: 11px; padding: 0px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word;&quot;&gt;1. Connect to WireGuard from any device (anywhere)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;font-size: 11px; padding: 0px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word;&quot;&gt;2. SSH into aegis and run wake-server.sh (only if AI server is off)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;font-size: 11px; padding: 0px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word;&quot;&gt;3. Open http://10.10.10.10:3000 in browser&lt;br&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;font-size: 11px; padding: 0px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word;&quot;&gt;4. All inference runs locally — no data leaves the network&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;pre style=&quot;overflow-x: auto; box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 4px; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 8px; background-color: light-dark(#ffffff, var(--ge-dark-color, #121212));&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: light-dark(rgb(255, 255, 255), transparent);&quot;&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;padding: 0px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;Monitoring &amp;amp; Alerting:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 0.9em;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;- LibreNMS on aeglero-host polls Pi, Switch, and host (SNMP)&lt;br&gt;- Cross-VLAN polls allowed by Pi UFW rule: 10.10.10.10 → :161/udp&lt;br&gt;- Alerts route via HTTPS POST → Discord webhook (encrypted)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="476" width="558" x="1028.87" y="9.5" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
